What is this game about?

Welcome to a world where ecology is under threat! Radioactive clouds have spread across the territory, and only you can clear the sky.
As a brave cleaner, you control a special vacuum that collects dangerous clouds and turns them into valuable resources.

Concept

You play as a hero running through the game world with a powerful vacuum cleaner. Your goal is to collect all radioactive clouds that appear in random locations.
The more clouds you collect, the more points you earn. With the points you accumulate, you can upgrade your vacuum, making it faster, stronger, and more efficient.

Game Mechanics

- Cloud Collection â€” run around the map and suck up radioactive clouds with your vacuum
- Resource Accumulation â€” earn points for every cloud you collect
- Upgrades â€” in the future, you'll be able to purchase vacuum upgrades (suction speed, range, power)

Controls

- WASD or arrow keys â€” character movement
- Left mouse button â€” interaction (cloud collection)
- ESC â€” return to menu

